[head=3]Job Request[/head]
Please mark below the job you would like to apply for.
You can chose multiple, by either numbering in priority or just with an x if you don't care which.

[color=red]Jobs with an asterisk requires a stamp to be approved. Some individuals may require additional approval[/color]
The following groups require approval for entry-level positions from their respective heads:
[/bullet] Cognizine'd entities of previous nonsentience
[/bullet] Previously unindentified individuals, like skeletons.
[/bullet] Visitors registered with a foreign vessel
[/bullet] Individuals with a criminal record
Furthermore, if there are many entry-level employees in one department, or if your previous department is understaffed, there may be some circumstances when further approval is required for an entry-level departmental transfer.
If there is no current head of the department in the Crew Manifest, then the Head of Personnel's stamp will suffice, except for positions in the Security Department.
The Captain's stamp can be used in place of any departmental head.

The following groups can not have a form of this type processed:
[/bullet] Unregistered visitors or unidentified individuals
[/bullet] Uncognizine animals of nonsentience
[/bullet] Prisoners, and individuals with a record of extreme or capital crimes.

